986
01:29:20,556 --> 01:29:21,853
Come on.

987
01:29:28,364 --> 01:29:30,264
Did you miss us?

988
01:29:30,332 --> 01:29:33,165
This girl's really
beginning to tick me off.

989
01:29:33,235 --> 01:29:35,635
<i>2 laps to go</i>
<i>in a two-car race.</i>

990
01:29:35,704 --> 01:29:39,265
<i>Trip Murphy and Maggie Peyton</i>
<i>will settle this between them!</i>

991
01:29:39,341 --> 01:29:41,468
Go, Maggie!

992
01:29:41,544 --> 01:29:43,603
- All right!
- We've got him now!

993
01:29:51,854 --> 01:29:52,878
On the outside!

994
01:29:53,923 --> 01:29:55,413
Go high, Herbie.

995
01:30:01,263 --> 01:30:03,390
Come on, Herbie.
We're almost there.

996
01:30:03,465 --> 01:30:07,458
<i>Door to door</i>
<i>off the corner at the final... Contact!</i>

997
01:30:07,536 --> 01:30:09,595
<i>Murphy slams</i>
<i>into the side of Peyton!</i>

998
01:30:15,911 --> 01:30:19,005
Mags, don't push it.
Mags, Herbie can't take it.

999
01:30:28,958 --> 01:30:32,257
- Forget the Bug and win!
- You're going down, Bug!

1000
01:30:39,101 --> 01:30:40,762
<i>Trouble in turn four!</i>

1001
01:30:40,836 --> 01:30:43,430
<i>Murphy into the wall</i>
<i>and upside down!</i>

1002
01:30:44,573 --> 01:30:48,509
OK, Herbie, you ready?

1003
01:30:48,577 --> 01:30:50,977
- Keep it steady!
- Ahh!

1004
01:30:51,046 --> 01:30:53,879
<i>No place to go!</i>
<i>Look out for the crash!</i>

1005
01:30:53,949 --> 01:30:55,917
<i>Herbie's...</i>

1006
01:30:56,018 --> 01:30:58,919
<i>Herbie's on the fence!</i>
<i>Herbie's on the fence!</i>

1007
01:31:04,159 --> 01:31:06,093
Oh! Oh, God!

1008
01:31:11,667 --> 01:31:13,567
<i>Maggie Peyton won!</i>

1009
01:31:13,636 --> 01:31:17,402
- <i>Maggie Peyton has won! Incredible!</i>
- <i>Unbelievable!</i>

1010
01:31:17,473 --> 01:31:19,998
<i>I've never seen anything</i>
<i>like this in NASCAR,</i>

1011
01:31:20,075 --> 01:31:23,636
<i>not to mention the birth</i>
<i>of the next great Peyton!</i>

1012
01:31:32,388 --> 01:31:35,880
We did it.

1013
01:31:39,862 --> 01:31:41,830
Let's go!

1014
01:31:41,897 --> 01:31:43,831
Whoo-hoo!

1015
01:32:05,921 --> 01:32:08,754
- Whoo!
- Yes!

1016
01:32:12,061 --> 01:32:14,495
I'm so proud of you!

1017
01:32:14,563 --> 01:32:16,622
Thanks, Dad.

1018
01:32:16,699 --> 01:32:18,326
Maggie, that was awesome!

1019
01:32:18,400 --> 01:32:21,233
- Thank you.
- So great!

1020
01:32:26,008 --> 01:32:28,306
Hey! I thought
your depth perception...

1021
01:32:28,377 --> 01:32:30,311
Oh, well,

1022
01:32:30,379 --> 01:32:33,473
the best Peyton was on
the track today. You did it.

1023
01:32:33,549 --> 01:32:36,416
- Congrats.
- Oh...

1024
01:32:36,518 --> 01:32:38,110
Look!
Listen to me!

1025
01:32:38,220 --> 01:32:39,812
That car is possessed!

1026
01:32:39,922 --> 01:32:41,321
Trip!

1027
01:32:42,658 --> 01:32:44,888
I saw it too.
It smiled at me!

1028
01:32:46,028 --> 01:32:47,825
That car is alive!

1029
01:32:47,896 --> 01:32:51,263
You gotta believe me.
It's mocking me!

1030
01:32:51,333 --> 01:32:53,801
I'm telling you!
That car is alive!

1031
01:32:55,904 --> 01:32:59,772
Look! It's doing it again!

1032
01:32:59,842 --> 01:33:02,936
You gotta believe me!
You gotta believe me!

1033
01:33:03,011 --> 01:33:04,808
