1034
01:33:04,880 --> 01:33:08,338
I'm going to get you, Bug!
I'm going to get you!

1035
01:33:08,450 --> 01:33:12,079
He's fine. He's fine.
Just a little dehydrated.

1036
01:33:13,322 --> 01:33:14,949
Wow.

1037
01:33:18,460 --> 01:33:21,588
Gotta say, Peyton, you and
Herbie make a great team.

1038
01:33:21,663 --> 01:33:23,995
We make a great team.

