a big race coming up.

1044
01:34:02,971 --> 01:34:06,532
Have her home at a decent hour.
Show some respect. All right?

1045
01:34:06,608 --> 01:34:08,405
My house, my rules.
<i>Comprende?</i>

1046
01:34:09,745 --> 01:34:12,009
OK, Ray,
I think they got it.

1047
01:34:12,080 --> 01:34:14,105
All right.

1048
01:34:14,183 --> 01:34:16,674
Go on. Get out of here.

1049
01:34:19,655 --> 01:34:21,623
I mean it, Herbie.

1050
01:34:27,062 --> 01:34:29,292
Rrrrr!

